cat << EOF
Enigma is a puzzle game inspired by Oxyd on the Atari ST and Rock'n'Roll on the Amiga. The object of 
the game is to find uncover pairs of identically colored Oxyd stones. Simple? Yes. Easy? Certainly 
not! Hidden traps, vast mazes, laser beams, and, most of all, countless hairy puzzles usually block 
your direct way to the Oxyd stones...
EOF
